author: Melissa Leon
title: Nancy Pelosi says people protesting stay-at-home orders is 'really unfortunate'
description: In her first interview on "Fox News Sunday" since 2017, House Speaker Nancy Pelosi, D-Calif., spoke to anchor Chris Wallace about the coronavirus pandemic and its effect on Americans.
